transcripts:
Exclusively for Bed Bath and Beyond, the Carlisle duvet cover and bedding collection by Wamsutta features a beautiful contemporary trellis pattern. The Carlyle duvet cover and pillow shams are 100% cotton, with a woven jacquard design. Coordinating pillow shams have the same trellis pattern as the duvet cover, resulting in a bed that is modern and uniquely sophisticated. 

Euro shams add an ideal backdrop to the bed. They are heavyweight cotton in a rich mocha color, and anchor the bedding ensemble. Decorative pillows add the key fashion elements that complete this elegant bed. 

The beautiful coordinating pillows accenting this bed suite are a soft velvet pillow in a rich shade of plum, a square taupe pillow with beautiful metallic embroidery, and an embroidered basket-weave pillow which adds texture to the bed. The Carlyle duvet cover embedding collection by Wamsutta is available exclusively online and at select Bed Bath and Beyond stores.
